quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,113,"Iyo hataba hejuru yawe imigisha y’Imana hamwe n’impuhwe zayo, ntankeka umurwi umwe muribo wari kwipfuza kugutakaza kandi nabo ntibari gutakaza atari imitima yabo gusa, kandi ntibazo shobora kukugirira inabi iyariyo yose, n’Imana niyo yakumanuriye igitabu gitagatifu hamwe n’ubuhizi n’ukukwereka ivyo utari uzi, n’imigisha y’Imana iri hejuru yawe nimininiya cane"
  4,114,"Ntamahoro arimwo muri vyinshi bumvikanyeko mu mabanga yabo atari bamwe bategeka abandi gutanga imperezwa canke kugira ineza canke guhuza hagati y’abantu, rero uwuzogira gutyo arondera impuhwe z’Imana uyo muntu tuzomuha impembo niniya cane"
  4,115,"Uwuzohakana intumwa y’Imana munyuma yaho yamaze kumu bonekera n’uburongozi hanyuma agakurikira inzira itari iyaba Isilamu, twebwe tuzomuhindura iyo azoba yahindukiriye kubwiwe, hanyuma duce tumwinjiza mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu naho n’ahantu habi cane haho umuntu atosubizwa mwo"